## Asset Helpers

### Images

```erb
<!-- In views -->
<%= image_tag "logo.png", alt: "Company Logo", class: "h-8" %>
<!-- Generates: <img src="/assets/logo-abc123.png" alt="Company Logo" class="h-8"> -->

<%= image_tag "icons/check.svg", class: "w-5 h-5" %>
<!-- Generates: <img src="/assets/icons/check-def456.svg" class="w-5 h-5"> -->

<!-- With specific dimensions -->
<%= image_tag "hero-background.jpg", 
    alt: "Hero background",
    class: "w-full h-96 object-cover",
    width: 1200,
    height: 600 %>
```

```css
/* In CSS */
.hero {
  background-image: url(/assets/hero-background.jpg);
}

.icon {
  background-image: url(/assets/icons/check.svg);
}
```

### Stylesheets

```erb
<!-- In layouts/application.html.erb -->
<%= stylesheet_link_tag "application", "data-turbo-track": "reload" %>
<!-- Generates: <link rel="stylesheet" href="/assets/application-abc123.css" data-turbo-track="reload"> -->

<!-- Additional stylesheets -->
<%= stylesheet_link_tag "admin", "data-turbo-track": "reload" %>
```

### JavaScript (via Importmap)

```erb
<!-- In layouts/application.html.erb -->
<%= javascript_importmap_tags %>
<!-- Generates importmap and module scripts -->
```

